Summary: Five red star like objects that were stationary than moved sideways and disappeared.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside looking at the sky, The objects were bright and blinking red and yellow. I thought they were helicopters at first but there was no sound. They were mostly stationary but moved side to side. I brought my kids out and it scared them and the UFO's moved to sideways and disappeared.
